43.body: JSON API endpoints are available for programmatic access to reports. üåê Public Access: All API endpoints are publicly accessible, no authentication required. See API.md for full documentation and usage examples. Weekly reports: https://news.free.technology/api/weekly/ Monthly reports: https://news.free.technology/api/monthly/ Latest: https://news.free.technology/api/weekly/latest.json Data is automatically pulled from various sources and added to this repo via an n8n pipeline . The pipeline runs every Friday , fetching all new data from the past week. You can view the workflow here .
